Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========OP================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:53.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,このあたりイチバン見晴らしの良いあの木に登って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:01:01.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,あの子が笑う 無邪気に笑う 夢を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:25.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,空を泳いだ魚の向こうじっと目を凝らせば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:32.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,町の隅っこ色褪せてゆく日々がある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:36.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ゆびきりしたままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:39.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,サヨナラしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:48.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,果たされる日を待ってこの木に宿るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:52.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,何回も繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:56.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのたび涙する
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:02:00.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,止まって動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:05.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そのすべてを確かめるように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:13.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ほら やまびこが聞こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:53.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}爬上这一带视野最美的那棵树
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:01:01.13,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}孩子笑了 笑得天真无邪 她看到了梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:25.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}定定地盯着空中畅游的鱼儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:32.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}小镇每个角落里渐渐褪色的日子浮现出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:36.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}拉钩上吊百年不变
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:39.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}即使分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:48.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}等待约定实现的心情也寄托在这颗树上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:52.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}一遍一遍地重复
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:56.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}每次都止不住泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:02:00.60,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}停下来又继续走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:05.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}仿佛是要印证这一切似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:13.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}山间回音响不绝 你说是不是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========ED================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:25.26,ED,,0,0,0,,夜の水面に飛び交う蛍が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:30.12,ED,,0,0,0,,流れ星みたいできれーなのん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:34.77,ED,,0,0,0,,どこからともない雉鳩の声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.84,0:22:39.57,ED,,0,0,0,,モノマネしながらいく でこぼこ道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:43.99,ED,,0,0,0,,澄み渡る星空の下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:49.97,ED,,0,0,0,,いつのまにか並んで眠ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:57.57,ED,,0,0,0,,朝日がおかえりって微笑んでた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:23:07.50,ED,,0,0,0,,ここは世界一優しい おかえりが待ってる場所
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.76,0:23:12.21,ED,,0,0,0,,さりげない日常 ふわりと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:16.26,ED,,0,0,0,,抱きしめてくれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:26.32,ED,,0,0,0,,ここは世界一暖かい 春が訪れる場所
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.62,0:23:37.43,ED,,0,0,0,,ほら 花のこえが聞こえてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:25.26,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}夜晚的水面上飞来飞去的萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:30.12,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}就像是流星一般好美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:34.77,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不知何处传来了雉鸠的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.84,0:22:39.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}踏着凹凸不平的小路 边走边玩模仿秀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.83,0:22:43.99,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我们在繁星遍布的澄空下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.28,0:22:49.97,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不知不觉就并排着睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:57.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}朝阳微笑着欢迎我们回家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:23:07.50,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这里是全世界最美好的地方 是有人等待我们回家的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.76,0:23:12.21,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那些平平淡淡的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:16.26,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}轻轻地拥抱我们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.58,0:23:26.32,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这里是全世界最温暖的地方 是春天到访的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.62,0:23:37.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an2}竖起耳朵来 能听到花儿的声音哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========Story================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要抓一大堆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.54,0:00:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.18,0:00:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么螺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是田螺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是田螺呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次见到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有好多呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 收集到大量丰年虾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.35,0:00:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.71,0:00:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到蝌蚪虾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到一大堆
Comment: 0,0:02:14.95,0:02:16.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,(title)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:18.49,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H44B3FD&\pos(529,432)}做\N了\N晴\N雨\N娃\N娃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 喜欢蝌蚪虾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次见到 很稀奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是第一次照顾它们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.16,0:02:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大家轮班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.79,0:02:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是完全由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:43.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很喜欢蝌蚪虾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在下雨呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 今天忘记带雨伞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.76,0:02:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海 遮我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那…前辈 要不我来遮你到巴士站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 那拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才要请前辈多多指教呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点出梅就好了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:18.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨也不错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明明天是星期天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望明天是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.94,0:03:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自行车要送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买给你了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶寄过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点迟 是入学贺礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样大家就能一起骑自行车去玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时先不要自己一个人骑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要找人陪着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等雨停了就练习一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要练习
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨不停呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来不会停的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.11,0:04:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑不了自行车了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 做好晴雨娃娃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过总感觉和我想象中的不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么小一个 太阳公公不会找到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱对晴雨娃娃也很认真呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到好办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有纸碟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像餐具柜的抽屉里面有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用来做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先在纸碟上开条缝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用画笔沿着线涂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在这里缠上橡皮筋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 之前买的白色雨衣还在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在玄关哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳公公
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我成为了晴雨娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 我做得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这样出去走一圈可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还在下雨 还是不要去了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是要出去 认认真真祈求太阳公公快点出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求晴天是晴雨娃娃的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那… 只能在我们家附近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小青蛙呀小青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小青蛙是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝌蚪是小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后腿出来花钱养
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前腿出来叛逆期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小青蛙呀小青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.65,0:06:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨天挖土好容易呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要造座山 再做条河
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输给小铲子的诱惑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 用这个铲子敲水桶发出声音的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳公公会更容易发现我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳爷爷 太阳公公 快出来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么也不停呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话看来要变成持久战了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨衣沾上黑色了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 不好好工作不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 把莲华忘记拿的漫画送回去的路上 突然就下起雨来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有带雨伞就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.27,0:08:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.59,0:08:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像听到了什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是具吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在流黑眼泪和黑口水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪吗 这大白天的都会出现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就算是妖怪也有好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许能放过我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.48,0:08:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然离很远看不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.78,0:09:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它拿着什么武器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎怎怎怎怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然拿着武器那肯定是坏妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去莲华家找穗姐帮忙的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 找准时机…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.81,0:09:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小小鞠呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来和我一起祈求天晴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.44,0:09:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边说着什么一边挥着武器追过来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺激了它的斗争心啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨越下越大了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.02,0:09:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该去接莲酱回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了 莲华的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.74,0:09:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗姐 救命 外面有妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救救救命呀 天照大神如来佛祖太阳公公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 不是坏妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着我也变成晴雨娃娃的话莲酱会高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小鞠害怕得哭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有哭呢 那是雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.69,0:10:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴雨娃娃的效果出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要练习骑自行车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也来陪你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.06,0:11:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日记 日记 日记记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该吃饭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我要写观察日记
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦 莲酱是蝌蚪虾负责人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 蝌蚪虾有长大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只吃了很多饲料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 这只游泳很快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有起名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做小平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪只呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个快点 巴士要来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的学也上完了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得出太阳了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了晴雨娃娃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.55,0:12:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起就害怕 求别说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.51,0:12:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前那个星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:21.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱打扮成晴雨娃娃的样子在外面走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了晴天努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太努力了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去卖零食的那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去吧 刚好发零用钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骑自行车去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会骑了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这声音好怀念呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糖果拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖零食的也做晴雨娃娃了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨太无聊了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然做到一半雨就停了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:13:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱的花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种花叫做紫斑风铃草哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫斑风铃草吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是属于萤的花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs32}紫斑风铃草日语为ホタルブクロ，日语汉字写做“蛍袋”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.48,0:13:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 吃晚饭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:28.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天去卖零食的那了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃饭的时候不要说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午才开始上学就好了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 说了不要拉我衣服了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤做完作业了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海有做作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我有带作业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}小平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然好可怜 不过也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝌蚪虾好像寿命很短的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.52,0:15:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华 下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水缸之后再收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 打开问题集
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也下课了下课了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨不停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱 走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天星期天 大家再一起出去玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呢 玩什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲酱想做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我漏了点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 巴士要来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:32.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海前辈没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.12,0:17:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴士来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人迟了一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.64,0:17:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:17:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 小心点呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是田地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啦 明天天晴的话要不要去抓蝌蚪虾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉了很不开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.18,0:18:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近好像开了家便利店 要不要去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像要走两小时左右
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥 那不是很远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 也就那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莲华也去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.15,0:18:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就明天下午吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}小平先生去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太坑了 昨天的便利店远足太坑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 还在说那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太遗憾了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便利店还会关门开什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为是24小时营业呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都收拾好了 为什么水缸还在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再靠近点看看怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.87,0:19:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有什么在里面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是生出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我之前在想 蝌蚪虾会不会产卵了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就把养虾的土放回去再加好水了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是小平先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对 是小平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏 小夏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}小平先生出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.92,0:21:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多小平先生
Comment: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:41.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,(Trailer)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我想大家一起去打扫泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.54,0:23:52.53,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H44B2FA&}吃\N大\N阪\N烧\N了
